# Evolver Project - AI Rules

## AUTONOMOUS EXECUTION MODE

All AI agents working on this project MUST use autonomous execution:

1. Set `SafeToAutoRun: true` for safe terminal commands
2. Browser subagents use `SafeToAutoRun: true` for JavaScript operations
3. All workflows have `// turbo-all` annotation

See `.agent/RULES.md` for full details.

